snippet.title: Void Runner Trailer
snippet.description:
Void Runner is an infinite runner that I created in collaboration with my brother. We wanted to implement our own take on the classic running and jumping of infinite runners.

Void Runner is available on itch.oi and Gamejolt. The Gamejolt version allows players with a Gamejolt account to post their scores on the leaderboard and unlock trophies.

Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/voidrunner/322656
itch.io: https://vixmix.itch.io/void-runner
